mmes susceptibles de vous inviter \u00e0 un entretien vid\u00e9o \u00e0 r\u00e9aliser sur la plateforme de recrutement EasyRecrue.<\/p>","link":{"url":"\/job\/candidature-spontanee-stages-f-h","title":"D\u00e9couvrir","target":"_self","internal":true},"postulate_link":{"url":"https:\/\/emea3.recruitmentplatform.com\/apply-app\/pages\/application-form?jobId=Q7SFK026203F3VBQB7V8N8MO5-142900&langCode=fr_FR","title":"Postuler","target":"_blank","internal":false},"company":{"image":{"src":"https:\/\/recrutement.bpce.fr\/app\/assets-bpce\/uploads\/2023\/09\/BANQUE_POPULAIRE_ACA_LOGO_2LD_RVB.png","alt":"Banque Populaire Aca Logo 2Ld Rvb"},"link":[]},"localisation":"Bordeaux","salaire_min":"","salaire_max":"","teletravail":"","localisations":[{"zipcode":"33100","region":"Nouvelle-Aquitaine","city":"Bordeaux","department":"Gironde","country":"France","address":"10 Quai des Queyries","localisation":"Bordeaux","coordinates":{"latitude":"44.842083","longitude":"-0.562802"}}]},{"post_id":147116,"job_number":"BPACAGA00067","advert_id":"261693","opening_id":"34395","modification_date":1766070095,"technical_id":["Q7SFK026203F3VBQB7V8N8MO5"],"liked":false,"title":"Candidature Spontan\u00e9e (F\/H)","date":"2017-11-12","datetime":"2017-11-12 23:00:","timestamp":1510527600,"sector":["Commercial"],"job":["Conseiller Client\u00e8le"],"jobcode":"01PAR202","jobcode_bpce":"","brand":["Banque Populaire Aquitaine Centre Atlantique"],"contract":["CDI"],"degree":["Bac +3"],"experience":["Confirm\u00e9"],"description":"<h2>Description de l'entreprise<\/h2><p><strong>Osez booster votre carri\u00e8re et venez vivre une nouvelle exp\u00e9rience collaborateur en int\u00e9grant notre entreprise !<\/strong><\/p> <p><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Nous valorisons les audaces et accompagnons les talents en\u00a0offrant des perspectives d\u2019\u00e9volution \u00e0 travers un parcours professionnel individualis\u00e9.<\/span><\/p> <p><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Rejoindre la Banque Populaire Aquitaine Centre-Atlantique, c'est aussi partager nos valeurs !<\/span><\/p> <p><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><em>#Proximit\u00e9 #Ecoute #AncrageR\u00e9gional #Espritd'Entreprendre #Performance <\/em><\/span><\/p> <p><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong>La Pr\u00e9f\u00e9rence Client c'est notre raison d'\u00eatre, c'est ce qui nous unit !<\/strong><\/span><\/p><h2>Profil et comp\u00e9tences requises<\/h2><p>Jeunes dipl\u00f4m\u00e9s ou professionnels exp\u00e9riment\u00e9s, issus d'une formation Bac+3 \u00e0 Bac+5, vous souhaitez exercer vos talents de commerciaux au sein d'une Banque R\u00e9gionale, alors rejoignez-nous!<\/p><h2>Informations compl\u00e9mentaires sur le poste<\/h2><p>Tous nos m\u00e9tiers sont ouverts aux personnes en situation de handicap.<\/p> <p>Dans le cadre de notre processus de recrutement, nous sommes susceptibles de vous inviter \u00e0 un entretien vid\u00e9o \u00e0 r\u00e9aliser sur la plateforme de recrutement EasyRecrue.<\/p>","link":{"url":"\/job\/candidature-spontanee-f-h","title":"D\u00e9couvrir","target":"_self","internal":true},"postulate_link":{"url":"https:\/\/emea3.recruitmentplatform.com\/apply-app\/pages\/application-form?jobId=Q7SFK026203F3VBQB7V8N8MO5-261693&langCode=fr_FR","title":"Postuler","target":"_blank","internal":false},"company":{"image":{"src":"https:\/\/recrutement.bpce.fr\/app\/assets-bpce\/uploads\/2023\/09\/BANQUE_POPULAIRE_ACA_LOGO_2LD_RVB.png","alt":"Banque Populaire Aca Logo 2Ld Rvb"},"link":[]},"localisation":"Bordeaux","salaire_min":"","salaire_max":"","teletravail":"","localisations":[{"zipcode":"33100","region":"Nouvelle-Aquitaine","city":"Bordeaux","department":"Gironde","country":"France","address":"10 Quai des Queyries","localisation":"Bordeaux","coordinates":{"latitude":"44.842083","longitude":"-0.562802"}}]},{"post_id":147154,"job_number":"CEAPCGA00002","advert_id":"5315266","opening_id":"2165131","modification_date":1766070089,"technical_id":["Q7SFK026203F3VBQB7V8N8MO5"],"liked":false,"title":"Candidatures Spontan\u00e9es","date":"2025-03-30","datetime":"2025-03-30 22:00:","timestamp":1743372000,"sector":["Commercial"],"job":["Charge de clientele particuliers"],"jobcode":"01PAR201","jobcode_bpce":"","brand":["Caisse d'Epargne Aquitaine Poitou Charentes"],"contract":["CDI"],"degree":["Bac +2"],"experience":["Jeune dipl\u00f4m\u00e9"],"description":"<h2>Description de l'entreprise<\/h2>Depuis 1818, la Caisse d\u2019Epargne est pionni\u00e8re dans les transitions de la soci\u00e9t\u00e9. Vous souhaitez contribuer \u00e0 son d\u00e9veloppement\u202f? Et si c\u2019\u00e9tait vous le prochain acteur de son ambition ? Appartenant au groupe BPCE, nous sommes le 2\u00e8me groupe bancaire fran\u00e7ais. Cela nous permet de cr\u00e9er des emplois durables et de vous offrir des opportunit\u00e9s de carri\u00e8re qui r\u00e9pondront \u00e0 vos projets ! \u202f Avec nos 2500 collaborateurs, aujourd\u2019hui, la Caisse d\u2019Epargne Aquitaine Poitou Charentes est une banque r\u00e9gionale, coop\u00e9rative, solide, puissante, qui couvre 9 d\u00e9partements. #proximit\u00e9 Ind\u00e9pendante des march\u00e9s financiers, la Caisse d\u2019Epargne Aquitaine Poitou Charentes appartient \u00e0 plus de 295 000 clients soci\u00e9taires en r\u00e9gion. #soci\u00e9tariat Trouver le juste \u00e9quilibre entre performance \u00e9conomique et engagement soci\u00e9tal\u202f: c\u2019est l\u00e0 tout l\u2019enjeu de notre d\u00e9marche de responsabilit\u00e9 soci\u00e9tale et environnementale. #rse. Pour cela, nous sommes pr\u00e9sents sur le march\u00e9 des particuliers (344 agences), des professionnels\u202f(14 agences), des entreprises (11 centres d\u2019affaires), des investisseurs mais aussi des collectivit\u00e9s locales. #coop\u00e9ratif. Fid\u00e8les \u00e0 nos valeurs coop\u00e9ratives, nous sommes engag\u00e9s dans une politique de ressources humaines responsable et volontariste. #inclusif. C\u2019est pour tout cela que nous souhaitons \u00ab\u202f\u00catre utile \u00e0 chacun, en \u00e9tant utile \u00e0 tous\u202f\u00bb\u202f!","link":{"url":"\/job\/candidatures-spontanees","title":"D\u00e9couvrir","target":"_self","internal":true},"postulate_link":{"url":"https:\/\/emea3.recruitmentplatform.com\/apply-app\/pages\/application-form?jobId=Q7SFK026203F3VBQB7V8N8MO5-5315266&langCode=fr_FR","title":"Postuler","target":"_blank","internal":false},"company":{"image":{"src":"https:\/\/recrutement.bpce.fr\/app\/assets-bpce\/uploads\/2023\/09\/CE_AQUIT_POITCHAR_LOGO_2021_LARGE_RVB.png","alt":"Ce Aquit Poitchar Logo 2021 Large Rvb"},"link":[]},"localisation":"Bordeaux","salaire_min":"","salaire_max":"","teletravail":"","localisations":[{"zipcode":"33076","region":"Nouvelle-Aquitaine","city":"Bordeaux","department":"Gironde","country":"France","address":"1 Parvis Corto Maltese","localisation":"Bordeaux","coordinates":{"latitude":"44.827947","longitude":"-0.551281"}}]}],"filters":{"list":[{"title":"Channel","id":"tax_channel","choices":[{"label":"Site BPCE","value":"q7sfk026203f3vbqb7v8n8mo5"}]},{"title":"Type de contrat","id":"tax_contract","choices":[{"label":"Alternance","value":"contrat-dapprentissage,contrat-en-alternance"},{"label":"CDD","value":"cdd"},{"label":"CDI","value":"cdi"},{"label":"Stage","value":"stage-sup-a-2-mois"}]},{"title":"Localisation","id":"tax_country","choices":[{"label":"France","value":"france"}]},{"title":"Famille de m\u00e9tier","id":"tax_sector","choices":[{"label":"Assurance","value":"assurance"},{"label":"Commercial","value":"commercial"},{"label":"Digital","value":"digital"},{"label":"Informatique","value":"informatique"},{"label":"Marketing, Animation commerciale & Communication","value":"marketing-animation-commerciale-communication-2"},{"label":"Organisation & Qualit\u00e9","value":"organisation-qualite-2"},{"label":"Ressources Humaines & Juridique","value":"ressources-humaines-juridique-2"},{"label":"Risques Controles et Engagements","value":"risques-controles-et-engagements"}]},{"title":"R\u00e9gion","id":"tax_place"